Watchdog Driver Error code
Watchdog Driver

The section has a list of all the error codes which are returned to the application. Base error code for the Watchdog module is defined in the include ti/common/mmwave_error.h. More...

Macros

#define WATCHDOG_EINVAL   (MMWAVE_ERRNO_WATCHDOG_BASE-1)
 Error Code: Invalid argument.
 
#define WATCHDOG_EINUSE   (MMWAVE_ERRNO_WATCHDOG_BASE-2)
 Error Code: Operation cannot be implemented because a previous operation is still not complete.
 
#define WATCHDOG_ENOTIMPL   (MMWAVE_ERRNO_WATCHDOG_BASE-3)
 Error Code: Operation is not implemented.
 

Detailed Description

The section has a list of all the error codes which are returned to the application. Base error code for the Watchdog module is defined in the include ti/common/mmwave_error.h.
